### ============================================
### 2. LOGIN DE CADA USUARIO
### ============================================

### 2.1 Login PRACTICANTE
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "juan.practicante@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Guarda el token que recibes como: TOKEN_PRACTICANTE

### 2.2 Login MAESTRO
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "carlos.maestro@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Guarda el token que recibes como: TOKEN_MAESTRO

### 2.3 Login PACIENTE
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.paciente@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Guarda el token que recibes como: TOKEN_PACIENTE

### ============================================
### 3. PERFIL DE CADA USUARIO
### ============================================

### 3.1 Ver perfil PRACTICANTE
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PRACTICANTE

### 3.2 Ver perfil MAESTRO
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO

### 3.3 Ver perfil PACIENTE
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PACIENTE

### ============================================
### 4. FUNCIONALIDADES DEL MAESTRO
### ============================================

### 4.1 Crear una práctica
POST http://localhost:3000/api/practices
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Práctica de Endodoncia Básica",
  "descripcion": "Introducción a los procedimientos de conducto radicular",
  "requisitos": "Haber cursado Anatomía Dental",
  "tipo_practica": "Endodoncia",
  "duracion_estimada_horas": 40,
  "cupo_maximo": 15,
  "fecha_inicio": "2025-02-01",
  "fecha_fin": "2025-06-30",
  "nivel_dificultad": "basico"
}

### 4.2 Ver todas mis prácticas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/practices
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO

### 4.3 Ver estadísticas de mis prácticas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/practices/statistics
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO

### 4.4 Asignar practicante a mi práctica (ID de práctica: 1, ID practicante: 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/practices/1/assign
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "practicante_id": 1
}

### 4.5 Ver practicantes asignados
GET http://localhost:3000/api/practices/1/practicantes
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO

### 4.6 Calificar a un practicante
POST http://localhost:3000/api/practices/1/practicantes/1/grade
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "calificacion": 9.5,
  "observaciones": "Excelente desempeño"
}

### ============================================
### 5. FUNCIONALIDADES DEL PRACTICANTE
### ============================================

### 5.1 Ver mis prácticas asignadas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/practices/my-practices/list
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PRACTICANTE

### 5.2 Ver todas las prácticas disponibles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/practices
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PRACTICANTE

### 5.3 Ver detalles de una práctica específica
GET http://localhost:3000/api/practices/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PRACTICANTE

### ============================================
### 6. FUNCIONALIDADES DEL PACIENTE
### ============================================

### 6.1 Ver su perfil
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PACIENTE

### 6.2 Cambiar su contraseña
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PACIENTE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Test123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPass123!"
}

### ============================================
### 7. CERRAR SESIÓN
### ============================================

### 7.1 Logout PRACTICANTE
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PRACTICANTE

### 7.2 Logout MAESTRO
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_MAESTRO

### 7.3 Logout PACIENTE
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_PACIENTE